</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="28" pageNumber="65" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="28.[151,1435,152,258]" pageId="28" pageNumber="65">
<emphasis box="[198,301,152,177]" italics="true" pageId="28" pageNumber="65">Remarks</emphasis>
: Illg (
<number box="[373,434,152,178]" pageId="28" pageNumber="65" value="1958.0">1958</number>
) was unable to determine the homology of the three pairs of retained mouthparts. We consider it likely that they represent the mandibles to maxillae, with the maxillipeds lacking, but confirmation of this must await the discovery of copepodid stages or males.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
